        "timestamp": "2020-05-05 16:17:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nRegarding adding of logging to context lib, it is not a good practice to log sensitive data. The handle is the key to a value pair in etcd. And also, this logs are in the normal execution path and they will fill up the trace/log buffers.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
