        "timestamp": "2020-05-06 22:45:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Regarding adding of logging to context lib, it is not a good practice to log sensitive data. The handle is the key to a value pair in etcd. And also, this logs are in the normal execution path and they will fill up the trace/log buffers.\n\nChanged such that all the logging is done at INFO level. So, in future, when we shall have log levels implemented, and we set the default log level to ERROR, these wont be displayed.",
        "patchset_number": 3
